::GoldenEye::

She smiled as he thanked her. She nodded to him and helped him walk.
"Like I said, if you need some energy, I have some you can have."  
She looked up at the sky and saw it was getting dark.  She knew they 
had an hour or so before it was dark.  "WE might want to stop for the 
night, unless you want to keep going."
